NAME
    Plack::Middleware::LastModified - Adds Last-Modified header
    automatically

SYNOPSIS
      builder {
          enable "LastModified";
          $app;
      };

DESCRIPTION
    Plack::Middleware::LastModified is a middleware that automatically adds
    "Last-Modified" header.

AUTHOR
    Masahiro Chiba

